00:43:43.176 --> 00:43:44.256
Ali.

00:43:44.296 --> 00:43:46.956
Dois noodles tom yum
e um com sopa clara.

00:43:47.136 --> 00:43:48.136
Obrigado!

00:43:59.576 --> 00:44:01.976
